A tool for converting dictionary files aka glossaries.

It support many formats: .csv .dtxt .epub .ifo .po .xdxf .xml .zim [...]
 See README.md for details about read and write.

NOTE: 4.6.1 is the latest version supported for Slackware since
the version of pyglossary greater than 4.6.1 use python-3.10.0+

Slackware (15.0) uses python-3.9.x as pyglossary-4.6.1 requires.

For full capability of software - install the optional dependencies:
 lxml beautifulsoup4 pyicu pyyaml python3-marisa-trie libzim python-lzo
 html5lib
